      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄘風·002.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">牆有茨.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>牆有茨，不可埽也，中冓之言，不可道也，所可道也，言之醜也。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The tribulus grows on the wall,
And cannot be brushed away.
The story of the inner chamber
Cannot be told.
What would have to be told
Would be the vilest of recitals.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
