      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄘風·002.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">牆有茨.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>牆有茨，不可襄也，中冓之言，不可詳也，所可詳也，言之長也。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The tribulus grows on the wall,
And cannot be removed.
The story of the inner chamber
Cannot be particularly related.
What might be particularly related
Would be a long story.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
