      <prop type="x-translation-ref">牆有茨.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>牆有茨，不可束也，中冓之言，不可讀也，所可讀也，言之辱也。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The tribulus grows on the wall,
And cannot be bound together and taken away.
The story of the inner chamber
Cannot be recited.
What might be recited
Would be the most disgraceful of things.</seg>
      </tuv>
